-- U.S. RESEARCH ROUNDUP-American Express, EZCORP, Zumiez
-- 
-- Thu Jul 10, 2014 05:58AM EDT
-- None



July 10 (Reuters) - Wall Street securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several U.S.-listed companies, including American Express and EZCORP, on Thursday.

HIGHLIGHTS * American Express <AXP.N>, CIT Group <CIT.N>: Macquarie starts with underperform ratings * World Acceptance <WRLD.O>, EZCORP <EZPW.O>: Macquarie starts with neutral  * Viacom <VIAB.O>: ISI Group raises target price to $100 from $95  Following is a summary of research actions on U.S. companies reported by Reuters on Thursday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.   * Alere <ALR.N>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to $50 from $45; rating buy  * American Express <AXP.N>, CIT Group <CIT.N>: Macquarie starts with underperform ratings * Cepheid <CPHD.O>: Wells Fargo starts with an outperform rating  * Discover Financial Services <DFS.N>: Macquarie starts with outperform rating * EZCORP <EZPW.O>: Macquarie starts with neutral ratings * Lumber Liquidators Holdings <LL.N>: Canaccord Genuity cuts target to $100 from $122; buy  * Potbelly <PBPB.O>: Piper Jaffray cuts price target to $14 from $19; overweight rating  * Qiagen <QGEN.O>: Wells Fargo starts with market perform ratings * Quidel <QDEL.O>: Wells Fargo starts with market perform ratings * Salix Pharmaceuticals <SLXP.O>: Leerink cuts target price to $160 from $162; outperform  * Santander Consumer USA <SC.N>: Macquarie starts with neutral * Springleaf Holdings <LEAF.N>: Macquarie starts with neutral * Tal International <TAL.N>: Macquarie starts with neutral * Textainer Group <TGH.N>: Macquarie starts with neutral ratings * Tractor Supply Co <TSCO.O>: RBC cuts target price to $69 from $78; rating outperform  * Viacom <VIAB.O>: ISI Group raises target price to $100 from $95; rating buy  * World Acceptance <WRLD.O>: Macquarie starts with neutral ratings * Zumiez Inc <ZUMZ.O>: D. A. Davidson raises price target to $36 from $35; rating buy   See bottom of the table for sector changes